<i>noun</i>: 포옹 [포ː옹], 파악 [파악], 투시 [투시], 이해심 [이ː해심 ], 이해력 [이ː해력], 이해 [이ː해], 영합 [영합], 양해 [양해], 납득 [납뜩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포옹 [포ː옹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hug; holding; embracing</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 품에 안거나 사람끼리 껴안음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of holding someone in one's arms or for two people to embrace each other.</dd><br>
<dd>2. acceptance; understanding</dd><br>
<dd>남을 넓은 마음으로 이해하고 품어 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of understanding and accepting someone with an open mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>파악 [파악]</dt><br>
<dd>understanding; identification; figuring out</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상의 내용이나 상황을 확실하게 이해하여 앎.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of getting to know something well, as one succeeds to understand the content or situation of a certain incident or subject.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>투시 [투시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. seeing through; penetration</dd><br>
<dd>막힌 물체를 꿰뚫어 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of seeing through a covered or blocked object.</dd><br>
<dd>2. understanding</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상의 속에 담겨 있는 의미까지 앎.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of understanding the hidden meaning of a certain subject.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이해심 [이ː해심 ]</dt><br>
<dd>understanding; sympathy</dd><br>
<dd>사정이나 형편을 알고 받아들이는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A mindset that knows and accepts someone's situation or circumstances.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이해력 [이ː해력]</dt><br>
<dd>ability to understand; understanding</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 깨달아 아는 힘. 또는 잘 알아서 받아들이는 힘.</dd><br>
<dd>The ability to realize and know something or to know and accept something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이해 [이ː해]</dt><br>
<dd>1. understanding; comprehension</dd><br>
<dd>무엇이 어떤 것인지를 앎. 또는 무엇이 어떤 것이라고 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of knowing what something is; the process of accepting something as something else.</dd><br>
<dd>2. understanding</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 깨달아 앎. 또는 잘 알아서 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having realized and knowing something; the process of knowing and accepting something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. understanding</dd><br>
<dd>남의 형편을 알고 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>The process of knowing and accepting someone's situation or circumstances.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영합 [영합]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flattery; adulation; ingratiation</dd><br>
<dd>개인적인 이익을 위해 마음에 없는 칭찬을 하며 따름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of praising someone without meaning it, for one's personal gains.</dd><br>
<dd>2. agreement; understanding</dd><br>
<dd>서로 뜻이 맞음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being of one mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>양해 [양해]</dt><br>
<dd>understanding; excuse</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 사정이나 잘못을 이해하고 너그럽게 받아들임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of understanding others' situation or fault, and taking it broad-mindedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>납득 [납뜩]</dt><br>
<dd>understanding</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 말이나 행동 등을 받아들이고 이해함.</dd><br>
<dd>Acceptance and understanding of someone's words or behavior.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>